-Use these as routing classes, not as guaranteed configured slugs:
-
-| Class | Best Route | Avoid |
-|---|---|---|
-| OpenAI reasoning/chat models | command center, research, final verification, multimodal/file review | blind implementation without repo context |
-| Anthropic Claude models | architecture critique, security review, senior reasoning | cheap bulk edits when cost matters |
-| Google Gemini models | long-context, multimodal, large artifact analysis | unsupported opencode direct execution |
-| xAI Grok models | current-source second opinion if web-enabled | final authority for repo changes without verification |
-| DeepSeek coding models | opencode coding execution, cheap/balanced implementation | final authority for high-risk review |
-| Qwen coding models | local/private coding, budget fallback, lightweight implementation | sole final reviewer for high-risk work |
-| Mistral/Codestral models | provider-diverse coding fallback, cost-aware code tasks | security-critical final authority without review |
-| Llama/Gemma/local open-weight models | local explanation, summarization, private drafts | production/security/destructive final authority |
-| Copilot-style IDE models | inline completion and editor suggestions | autonomous repo-agent primary route |
