-## Prompt Construction Rules
-
-The `Prompt to Use` must:
-
-- Restate the task boundaries.
-- Tell the selected model what to do and what not to do.
-- Include safety/approval gates when applicable.
-- Require explicit assumptions, changed files, test plan, and rollback notes for implementation tasks.
-- Require source checking for current-research tasks.
-- Require no file edits for review-only tasks.
-- Keep local/private constraints visible when privacy mode is local-preferred or local-required.
