-## Route Examples
-
-### Example 1: Small docs edit
-
-Primary: DeepSeek V4 Flash. Backup: DeepSeek V4 Pro. Final reviewer: ChatGPT/OpenAI. Risk: Low. Approval: No.
-
-### Example 2: Auth/session refactor
-
-Primary: Claude for plan/review, then DeepSeek V4 Pro for implementation after approval. Backup: ChatGPT/OpenAI. Final reviewer: Claude + ChatGPT/OpenAI. Risk: High. Approval: Yes.
-
-### Example 3: Latest provider/model comparison
-
-Primary: ChatGPT/OpenAI with current research. Backup: Gemini or Grok if web-enabled. Final reviewer: ChatGPT/OpenAI. Current Research Needed: Yes. Approval: No unless implementing changes.
-
-### Example 4: Private local docs/code draft
-
-Primary: Qwen-Coder local. Backup: DeepSeek V4 Flash if cloud allowed. Final reviewer: ChatGPT/OpenAI for non-trivial work. Risk: Low/Medium. Approval depends on file edits.
